trans-unit.source: Encapsulates the collection of <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Image" /> objects in an <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList" />.
trans-unit.target: Encapsula a coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Image" /> em um <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList" />.

trans-unit.source: This is used to manage the images in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList> programmatically, providing methods to add and remove image objects.
trans-unit.target: Isso é usado para gerenciar as imagens no <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList> programaticamente, fornecimento de métodos para adicionar e remover objetos de imagem.

trans-unit.source: The following code example shows how to select, remove, and display images, from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.Images%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList> class, which is an <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.ImageCollection> type.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir mostra como selecionar, remover e exibir imagens, do <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.Images%2A> propriedade o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList> classe, que é um <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.ImageCollection> tipo.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified object to the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList" />.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona o objeto especificado ao <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Icon" /> to add to the list.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Icon" /> para ser adicionado à lista.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified icon to the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList" />.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona o ícone especificado ao <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Icon> is converted to a <xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap> before it is added to the list.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Drawing.Icon> é convertido em um <xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap> antes de ser adicionado à lista.

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates constructing an <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.%23ctor%2A>, adding images to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.Images%2A> property, setting the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.ImageSize%2A> property, and using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.Draw%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir demonstra a construir um <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.%23ctor%2A>, adicionando imagens para o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.Images%2A> configuração da propriedade, o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.ImageSize%2A> propriedade e usando o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.Draw%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: To run this example, place it in a form that contains a button named `Button1`.
trans-unit.target: Para executar este exemplo, coloque-o em um formulário que contém um botão chamado `Button1`.

trans-unit.source: The example assumes the existence of FeatherTexture.bmp and Gone Fishing.bmp at c:\Windows\\.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo supõe a existência de FeatherTexture.bmp e Fishing.bmp não existe mais em c:\Windows\\.

trans-unit.source: Change the example accordingly if the bitmaps do not exist on your system or exist at another location.
trans-unit.target: Altere o exemplo se os bitmaps existe no sistema ou em outro local.
